Package cdx.opencdx.client.service

Interface OpenCDXAuditClient

All Known Implementing Classes:
OpenCDXAuditClientImpl
public interface OpenCDXAuditClient
Audit Service for interfacing to the service. Used for both direct gRPC client and Message based Client.
